2%8COpenFeign"><span class="nav-number">0.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">feign和OpenFeign</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#OpenFeign%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8"><span class="nav-number">1.</span> <span class="nav-text">OpenFeign服务调用</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3-%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3"><span class="nav-number">1.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">接口+注解</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#OpenFeign%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6"><span class="nav-number">2.</span> <span class="nav-text">OpenFeign超时控制</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#OpenFeign%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD"><span class="nav-number">3.</span> <span class="nav-text">OpenFeign日志打印功能</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#Hystrix%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8"><span class="nav-number"></span> <span class="nav-text">Hystrix服务调用</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B"><span class="nav-number">1.</span> <span class="nav-text">案例:</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#Jmeter%E5%8E%8B%E6%B5%8B%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95"><span class="nav-number">1.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">Jmeter压测测试</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3"><span class="nav-number">1.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">解决</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%8D%E7%BA%A7"><span class="nav-number"></span> <span class="nav-text">服务降级</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%8D%E7%BA%A7"><span class="nav-number">1.</span> <span class="nav-text">全局服务降级</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98"><span class="nav-number">1.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">目前问题:</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98"><span class="nav-number">1.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">解决问题:</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%80%9A%E9%85%8D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E9%99%8D%E7%BA%A7FeignFallback"><span class="nav-number">2.</span> <span class="nav-text">通配服务降级FeignFallback</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%86%94%E6%96%AD"><span class="nav-number"></span> <span class="nav-text">服务熔断</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%86%94%E6%96%AD%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0"><span class="nav-number">0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">熔断机制概述</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">案例：</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#Hystrix%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E5%8C%96DashBoard"><span class="nav-number">0.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">Hystrix图形化DashBoard</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div>
