<h4 id="Ribbon负载均衡算法"><a href="#Ribbon负载均衡算法" class="headerlink" title="Ribbon负载均衡算法"></a>Ribbon负载均衡算法</h4><p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AE%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%843/1596786871454.png" alt="1596786871454"></p>
